1.title: Who's Your Doggie?
1.plot: Ever meet a dog and wonder what breed it is? We did, and now we�۪ve got the answer. Using one of the most reliable DNA labs in the world, we reveal the breeds of six very mixed-up mutts���and the results will shock you. With an almost endless list of breed combinations, What Breed Am I? covers the big, the small, the cute and the downright crazy.

10.title: World's Greatest Dogs
10.plot: From highly skilled acrobatics to breathtaking stunts... from skateboarding to riding a scooter... from rope jumping to surfing... These are the stories of the World's Greatest Dogs. Marvel at amazing canine tricks and action-packed performances. Witness how some underdogs turned from rejected puppy to thriving stars. This special celebrates the most extraordinary dogs - and their dedicated owners - that hold world titles for all kind of talents.

imdb.plot outline: Nat Geo WILD celebrates pawsome dogs with its inaugural BarkFest weekend, kicking off Friday, April 14. It's a weekend of all bark, no bite TV featuring some of the smartest, most unique and cutest canines in the world. There will be surfing dogs, service dogs, games to find out if your dog is a genius, Cesar Millan marathons and much more. Calling all dog lovers.
